729370f-b.title: Richmond: Richmond Road - Liberty Avenue
729370f-b.text:
(1)
1622 Richmond Road, at the S. E. corner of
Liberty Avenue, showing the Egbert House. lIt was
the house of Joseph Egbert, Congressman for one
term, and County Clerk for one year in 1869. It
is a Colonial dwelling. The view is north.
Yinter, 1925
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2)
The same, looking south.
Winter, 1925
P. L. Sperr
NO REiRODUCTIONS
(3)
The rear of the Echert House.
1924
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
